Easy Bean and Cheese Burrito

15 min
$5
600 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Tags:

Description

A quick and satisfying burrito filled with creamy refried beans and melty cheese, perfect for any meal!

Ingredients

  • flour tortillas: 2 large
  • refried beans: 1 cup
  • shredded cheddar cheese: 1 cup
  • sour cream: optional, for serving
  • salsa: optional, for serving
